## Scoring Guide
- **9-10**: Professional quality, ready for publication
- **7-8**: Strong work, minor improvements possible
- **5-6**: Solid foundation, notable issues to address
- **3-4**: Significant problems, needs revision
- **1-2**: Fundamental issues, consider rewriting
